{"tid":2319810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"焼肉ライク ...又係比咗美心","createTime":"2020-12-10T10:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T11:46:49.000Z","uid":261919,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91993cd3fba1c5862b474d9965f0d1d3089ab8ab","tid":2319810,"uid":261919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒：日本集團與香港簽約消息<br />\n<br />\n本年1月底據日媒報導及集團官方的宣布指：「ダイニングイノベーショングループ（DINING INNOVATION ASIA-PACIFIC PTE LTD. ，以下DIAP） 集團首次決定進駐越南、泰國和香港。我們與香港最大的餐飲集團Maxim簽訂了「焼肉ライク」在香港和泰國的特許經營合同。目標是加強在亞洲地區的店鋪開設。」又指：「預計在2020年年內進駐泰國曼谷及香港。」DIAP解釋與香港美心集團合作的原因是因為香港美心集團於1956年在香港成立，除了香港和中國的各種餐飲業務外，業務更擴展至越南、柬埔寨和泰國等國家和地區，集團開設了多達980間店舖，因此與其合作可以通過雙方的網絡來加速集團的海外業務發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/yakiniku-like-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fyakiniku-like-hk%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYprPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=c5737ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/yakiniku-like-hk/</a>"},{"pid":"cc6e6429109ab7c6d67e6f98450a6fc8033b0e5e","tid":2319810,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"焼肉ライク<br />\nfacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yakinikulike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyakinikulike&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYprPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=10eebb77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yakinikulike</a><br />\ntwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/like_yakiniku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flike_yakiniku&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYprPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=199afc88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/like_yakiniku</a>"},{"pid":"0ca1afaa26ee34736612bc610aa6c062444870be","tid":2319810,"uid":60434,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"黃屍又唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/